rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Agent properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators with the domain of RDA Agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by shortening or condensing the original work but leaving the nature and content of the original work substantially unchanged to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is actor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to an expression of a work by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addresseeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addressee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body to whom a work or part of a work is addressed to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressOfTheCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has address of the corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to the address of a corporate body’s headquarters or offices, or an e-mail or internet address for the body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressOfThePerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has address of the person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to the address of a person’s place of residence, business, or employer, and/or an e-mail or internet address.

rdf:Description.reg:name: affiliation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has affiliation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a group with which a person is affiliated or has been affiliated through employment, membership, cultural identity, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternateIdentity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternate identity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a pseudonymous or other identity assumed by the person.

rdf:Description.reg:name: animatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is animator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a moving image work or computer program by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is annotator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person who makes manuscript annotations on an item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantCorporateBodyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellant corporate body of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body who appeals a lower court's decision to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person or corporate body who appeals a lower court's decision to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantPersonOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellant person of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person who appeals a lower court's decision to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleeCorporateBodyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellee corporate body of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body against whom an appeal is taken to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person or corporate body against whom an appeal is taken to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleePersonOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellee person of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person against whom an appeal is taken to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: architectOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is architect of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building, etc. to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangerOfMusicOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arranger of music of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a musical work by rewriting the composition for a medium of performance different from that for which the work was originally intended to the expression.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: An arranger of music may also modify the work for the same medium of performance, etc., keeping the musical substance of the original composition essentially unchanged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is art director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by overseeing the artists and craftspeople who build the sets for moving image productions to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work by conceiving, and often implementing, an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc. to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: associatedInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has associated institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to an institution commonly associated with a corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: authorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is author of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work that is primarily textual in content, regardless of media type (e.g., printed text, spoken word, electronic text, tactile text) or genre (e.g., poems, novels, screenplays, blogs) to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is autographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person whose manuscript signature appears on an item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binderOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is binder of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person who binds an item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: biographicalInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has biographical information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to information about the life or history of a person.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is book designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in manufacturing a manifestation by being responsible for the entire graphic design of a book, including arrangement of type and illustration, choice of materials, and process used to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: brailleEmbosserOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is braille embosser of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in manufacturing a manifestation by embossing braille cells using a stylus, special embossing printer, or other device to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcasterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is broadcaster of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in broadcasting a manifestation to an audience via radio, television, webcast, etc to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographerExpressionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cartographer (expression) of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing additional cartography, or by modifying the previous cartography to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cartographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a map, atlas, globe, or other cartographic work to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: casterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is caster of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in manufacturing a manifestation by pouring a liquid or molten substance into a mold and leaving it to solidify to take the shape of the mold to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographerExpressionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreographer (expression) of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by providing additional choreography, or by modifying the previous choreography to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work of movement to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectionRegistrarOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collection registrar of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate work such as a collection of items or works to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collector of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collotyperOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collotyper of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in manufacturing a manifestation of photographic prints from film or other colloid that has ink-receptive and ink-repellent surfaces to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to an expression of a work by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compilerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is compiler of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a new work (e.g., a bibliography, a directory) by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc. to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composerExpressionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is composer (expression) of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression by adding music to a work that originally lacked it, by composing new music to substitute for the original music, or by composing new music to supplement the existing music to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is composer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a musical work to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: conductorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is conductor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to an expression of a musical work by leading a performing group (orchestra, chorus, opera, etc.) in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: consultantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is consultant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for another person, family or corporate body that is represented as the creator of a work to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression to the expression.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Contributors include editors, translators, arrangers of music, performers, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: corporateHistory
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has corporate history
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to historical information about the corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: costumeDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is costume designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by designing the costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: countryAssociatedWithThePerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has country associated with the person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a country with which a person is identified.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtGovernedOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is court governed of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature (e.g., laws, administrative regulations) to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtReporterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is court reporter of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by preparing a court's opinions for publication to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: creatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is creator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the creation of a work to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is curator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body conceiving, aggregating, and/or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwnerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is current owner of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body currently having legal possession of an item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodianOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is custodian of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body having legal custody of an item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dancerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dancer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to an expression of a work by dancing in a musical, dramatic, etc., presentation to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateAssociatedWithTheCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date associated with the corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to the date or range of dates on which a conference, etc., was held, or a date with which a corporate body is otherwise associated (e.g., date of founding).

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateAssociatedWithTheFamily
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date associated with the family
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to a significant date associated with a family.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateAssociatedWithThePerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date associated with the person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a significant date associated with a person (e.g., date of birth, date of death).

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfBirth
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of birth
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to the year a person was born.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Date of birth may also include the month or month and day of the person’s birth.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfConferenceEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of conference, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to the date or range of dates on which a conference, congress, meeting, exhibition, fair, festival, etc., was held.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfDeath
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of death
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to the year a person died.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Date of death may also include the month or month and day of the person’s death.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfEstablishment
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of establishment
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to the date on which a corporate body was established or founded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfTermination
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of termination
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to the date on which a corporate body was terminated or dissolved.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicateeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dedicatee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body to whom a work is dedicated to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicateeOfItemOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dedicatee of item of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body to whom an item is dedicated to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dedicator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body by whom a work is dedicated to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: defendantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is defendant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person or corporate body who is accused in a criminal proceeding or sued in a civil proceeding to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeGrantingInstitutionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is degree granting institution of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body granting an academic degree to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeSupervisorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is degree supervisor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person overseeing a higher-level academic degree to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: depositorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is depositor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a current owner of an item who deposited the item into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descendantFamily
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has descendant family
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to a family descended from the other family.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descendants
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has descendants
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a family descended from the particular person.

rdf:Description.reg:name: designerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a design for an object to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc. to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOfPhotographyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of photography of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body that captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges the lighting to the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The director of photography for a movie is also called the chief cinematographer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is distributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for distributing a resource to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: donorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is donor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a former owner of an item who donated that item to another owner to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: draftsmanOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is draftsman of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by an architect, inventor, etc., by making detailed plans or drawings for buildings, ships, aircraft, machines, objects, etc. to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is editor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by revising or clarifying the content, e to the expression.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: An editor may also prepare an expression of a work for production, publication, or distribution.

rdf:Description.reg:name: editorOfMovingImageWorkOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is editor of moving image work of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for assembling, arranging, and trimming film, video, or other moving image formats, including both visual and audio aspects to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: employee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has employee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person employed by the corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: employer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has employer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a corporate body that employs the person.

rdf:Description.reg:name: enactingJurisdictionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is enacting jurisdiction of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a jurisdiction enacting a law, regulation, constitution, court rule, etc. to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: engraverOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is engraver of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in manufacturing a manifestation by cutting letters, figures, etc., on a surface such as a wooden or metal plate used for printing to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: etcherOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is etcher of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in manufacturing a manifestation by subjecting metal, glass, or some other surface used for printing, to acid or another corrosive substance to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: familyHistory
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has family history
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to biographical information about the family and its members.

rdf:Description.reg:name: familyMember
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has family member
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to a person who is a member of the family.

rdf:Description.reg:name: fieldOfActivityOfTheCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has field of activity of the corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a field of business in which a corporate body is engaged and/or the body's area of competence, responsibility, jurisdiction, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: fieldOfActivityOfThePerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has field of activity of the person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a field of endeavour, area of expertise, etc., in which a person is engaged or was engaged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is film director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmDistributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is film distributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body involved in distributing a moving image manifestation to theatres or other distribution channels to the manifestation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmmakerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is filmmaker of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating an independent or personal film to the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A filmmaker is individually responsible for the conception and execution of all aspects of the film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmProducerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is film producer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a producer responsible for most of the business aspects of a film to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formerOwnerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is former owner of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body formerly having legal possession of an item to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: foundedCorporateBodyOfCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founded corporate body of corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a corporate body that the other corporate body founded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: foundedCorporateBodyOfFamily
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founded corporate body of family
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to an organization that the family founded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: foundedCorporateBodyOfPerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founded corporate body of person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to an organization that the person founded.

rdf:Description.reg:name: founder
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person who founded the corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: foundingCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founding corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a corporate body that founded the other corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: foundingFamily
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has founding family
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a family that founded the corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: fullerFormOfName
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has fuller form of name
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to the full form of a part of a name represented only by an initial or abbreviation in the form chosen as the preferred name, or a part of the name not included in the form chosen as the preferred name.

rdf:Description.reg:name: gender
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has gender
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to the gender with which a person identifies.

rdf:Description.reg:name: groupMember
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has group member
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person who is a member of the performing group, expedition, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: groupMemberOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has group member of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a corporate body (performing group, expedition, etc.) of which the person is a member.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hereditaryTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has hereditary title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to a title of nobility, etc., associated with a family.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hierarchicalSubordinate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has hierarchical subordinate
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a corporate body that is subordinate to the other corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hierarchicalSuperior
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has hierarchical superior
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a corporate body that is hierarchically superior to the other corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honoureeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is honouree of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body honoured by a work (e.g., the honouree of a festschrift) to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honoureeOfItemOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is honouree of item of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body honoured by an item, e to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hostInstitutionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is host institution of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body hosting the event, exhibit, conference, etc to the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: hostOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is host of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to an expression of a work by leading a program (often broadcast) that includes other guests, performers, etc. (e.g., talk show host) to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForTheCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a character string uniquely associated with a corporate body, or with a surrogate for a corporate body (e.g., an authority record).
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The identifier serves to differentiate that corporate body from other corporate bodies.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForTheFamily
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the family
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a family to a character string uniquely associated with a family, or with a surrogate for a family (e.g., an authority record).
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The identifier serves to differentiate that family from other families.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForThePerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person to a character string uniquely associated with a person, or with a surrogate for a person (e.g., an authority record).
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The identifier serves to differentiate that person from other persons.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illuminatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illuminator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person providing decoration to a specific item using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs to the item.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustratorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a person, family, or corporate body contributing to an expression of a work by supplementing the primary content with drawings, diagrams, photographs, etc to the expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incumbent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has incumbent
